name: Green Star
description: Invested by Softbank Group (USA), Friends of the Earth (HK) and World Wide Fund for Nature, $GRCC aims to build a green and environmentally friendly parallel metaverse world. Project Greenstar (GRCC) is currently pancakeswap and poocoin is also a welcome gaming token. It is a game based on returning to the days again and again with the climate green crisis. You can benefit from the tree on renting or buying land. You can rent the lands you can benefit from and earn a profit.
